Name: Agent Focus: Corin
Desc: Use it to obtain the Agent or unlock the Agent's Mindscapes.
Desc2:
Snapshots from Corin's daily life and from in combat, recording important moments before and after she became an Agent.
These images also provide insights into her fighting style and favorite weapons, helping to better understand her strengths.

A carefully-wrapped present with a bow on the box. But the edge of this ribbon... What has it been cut with?
